      "file_path": "bpmn/so-bpmn-infrastructure-common/src/test/java/org/onap/so/bpmn/infrastructure/pnf/delegate/CreatePnfEntryInAaiDelegateTest.java",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 45,
      "message": "1. Lack of consistency in mockito API usage. Since the sections are marked as given/when/then comments, do not use Mockito.when, but rather opt to use a pure BDD approach by using BDDMockito.given\n\n2. Suggestion - instead of harcoding the UUID test value, consider generating it deterministically. Also avoid duplication.",
